data.description: Gorgeous Chalet is the main house w/floor to ceiling windows facing the beautiful Rock Creek. Kitchen has large breakfast bar island, huge pantry, skylight and gas cookstove. Primary is on main w/private deck and hot tub. Enjoy great views from the upstairs loft. Separate guest quarters offer 1bd, 1ba in 720sqft of private space for visitors. Tinker in the workshop. RV parking w/2 carports available, chicken coop, goat pen, grapes, fruit & nut trees, private beach w/swimming hole. Brand new comp roofs! Lot line adjustment to creek has been approved and recorded. Back on the market just in time for you to call this your new summer oasis!
